TY  - JOUR
TI  - Product Durability under Monopoly and Competition
AU  - Kamien, Morton I.
AU  - Schwartz, Nancy L.
AB  - [The durabilities of a consumption good produced in a perfectly competitive market or by a monopoly are compared. The analysis is conducted in terms of firm profit maximization in a Cournot industry. Conclusions are based on the properties of the entire optimal path rather than on the steady state alone.]
